---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`Security Compliance - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Understanding New Zealand security frameworks including NZISM and Protective Security Requirements for organizational security planning." />

<Header />
<main>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Security Compliance Guidance</h1>
			<p class="tagline">Understanding New Zealand's Security Framework Requirements</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="compliance-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro">
				<p>Navigating New Zealand's security compliance landscape requires understanding key government frameworks. We help organizations comprehend these requirements and identify appropriate security solutions.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="framework-overview">
				<h2>Understanding Key Security Frameworks</h2>
				
				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>NZISM (New Zealand Information Security Manual)</h3>
					<p>The government's comprehensive manual for protecting official information. It outlines security controls, risk management approaches, and technical requirements for government agencies and their partners.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We help interpret NZISM requirements and identify commercial solutions that align with its security objectives.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>Protective Security Requirements (PSR)</h3>
					<p>An all-of-government framework covering personnel, physical, and information security measures for protecting sensitive government information.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We provide guidance on PSR alignment and recommend security practices that support compliance objectives.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="framework-item">
					<h3>International Security Standards</h3>
					<p>Various international standards and certifications recognized within New Zealand security frameworks, including FIPS 140-2, Common Criteria, and other validation programs.</p>
					<div class="our-role">
						<strong>Our Approach:</strong> We help identify products with relevant certifications that may support your security and compliance goals.
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="capabilities">
				<h2>How We Can Assist</h2>
				<div class="capability-grid">
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Framework Education</h3>
						<p>Helping your team understand NZISM, PSR, and other relevant security requirements and how they apply to your organization.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Solution Identification</h3>
						<p>Recommending commercially available security products and solutions that align with framework requirements.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="capability">
						<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
						<p>Assisting with the deployment and configuration of security solutions in your environment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="disclaimer-box">
				<h3>Important Information</h3>
				<p><strong>Hermetrix Technologies provides advisory services and implementation support for security solutions.</strong> We are not a government agency and cannot provide official compliance certifications or security clearances.</p>
				<p>Formal compliance status, security accreditations, and government approvals must be obtained through the appropriate official channels. We support your journey toward compliance through education and appropriate solution implementation.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Need to Understand Compliance Requirements?</h2>
				<p>Contact us to discuss how we can help your organization navigate security framework requirements.</p>
				<div class="contact-methods">
					<a href="mailto:hello@hermetrix.nz" class="btn primary">General Inquiry</a>
					<a href="mailto:security@hermetrix.nz" class="btn secondary">Framework Consultation</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
<Footer />

<style>
	/* Full-screen layout */
	body {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	main {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	/* Hero Section - Full viewport */
	.hero {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a1a 50%, #2a2a2a 100%);
		color: white;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		width: 100vw;
		margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
	}

	.hero::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
					radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.hero > .container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: 5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 900;
		color: #ffffff;
		text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5), 0 0 60px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
	}

	/* Compliance Content - Full screen sections */
	.compliance-content {
		flex: 1;
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: var(--bg-secondary);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 100vh;
	}

	.intro {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}

	.framework-overview {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.framework-overview h2 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.framework-item {
		background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.framework-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-dark));
	}

	.framework-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 45px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
		border-color: var(--accent);
	}

	.framework-item h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.framework-item p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.our-role {
		background: rgba(56, 178, 172, 0.1);
		border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(56, 178, 172, 0.3);
		font-size: 1rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(56, 178, 172, 0.1);
	}

	.our-role strong {
		color: #38b2ac;
		text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(56, 178, 172, 0.5);
	}

	.capabilities {
		max-width: 1400px;
		margin: 0 auto 5rem;
	}

	.capabilities h2 {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		font-size: 3rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.capability-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.capability {
		background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
		border-radius: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.capability:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
		border-color: var(--accent);
	}

	.capability h3 {
		color: var(--text-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.capability p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.disclaimer-box {
		background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
		border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		margin: 4rem auto;
		max-width: 1200px;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
	}

	.disclaimer-box h3 {
		color: #ffc107;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.5);
	}

	.disclaimer-box p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: var(--bg-primary);
		color: white;
		min-height: 60vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.cta-section p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #0a0a0a;
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dark);
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--accent);
		border-color: var(--accent);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #0a0a0a;
		box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.container {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: none;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 4rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.framework-overview h2,
		.capabilities h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
			min-height: 90vh;
		}
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.compliance-content {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
			min-height: auto;
		}
		.intro {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}
		.framework-overview {
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}
		.framework-overview h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}
		.capabilities h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}
		.contact-methods {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
		.btn {
			width: 250px;
		}
		.capability-grid,
		.framework-item {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}
		.cta-section {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
			min-height: auto;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}
		.framework-overview h2,
		.capabilities h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.cta-section h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.btn {
			padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
